zooproject

Class Enclosure

  • java.lang.Object
    • zooproject.Enclosure

  • public class Enclosure
extends java.lang.Object
    Enclosure class is where Animals will live inside. The Enclosure also has a Foodstore containing varying amounts of food in it, potentially of different types. The Zookeepers will fill the Foodstore from the Zoo Foodstore. Each Enclosure will also accrue a certain amount of Animal waste.
